{"tid":1876114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【冚球產】巴西出現9成基因無法識別新病毒 尼日利亞15人48小時內不治","createTime":"2020-02-12T07:57:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T10:25:10.000Z","uid":46685,"like":189,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":114,"replies":[{"pid":"43bce9569f9d8f026b3d1a2552d471b3e0dfd5a3","tid":1876114,"uid":46685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T07:57:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bRkob1F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbRkob1F.jpg&h=c89d1c28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當被稱為「武漢肺炎」的新型冠狀病毒在全球蔓延之時，有科學家在巴西一個人造湖中，發現了一種從未見過的神秘新病毒，暫命為「雅拉病毒」（Yaravirus brasiliensis）。科學家發現，在目前已知的基因排序組合中，雅拉病毒90%基因無法被配對及識別出來，研究人員憂心，病毒恐怕存在巨大變異性。<br />\n<br />\n據Science Alert報道，新病毒是在巴西人工湖Lake Pampulha被發現，大約由80納米大小的粒子組成。由法國病毒學家Bernard La Scola及巴西病毒學家J&ocirc;natas S. Abrah&atilde;o組成團隊進行研究，以巴西神話的水神雅拉（Yara）命名為「雅拉病毒」。<br />\n<br />\n研究人員亦指出，「雅拉病毒」並非用複雜基因組合呈現，但是就帶有大量過去未曾發現的基因。近幾年科學家發現病毒變異，變異形式開始令人思考病毒是如何傳播，或存有甚麼作用。<br />\n<br />\n近日武漢肺炎肆虐全球，單單內地確診個案已突破4萬宗，而內地死亡個案亦逾千宗，外國不少國家都有確診個案。一波未平，一波又起，非洲尼日利亞爆發不明疫症，在不足一週內造成過百人感染，15人死亡，所有死者都在染病後48內死亡。<br />\n<br />\n104人染病　15人亡<br />\n<br />\n綜合外國傳媒，引述尼日利亞參議員消息，當地截至上周一（3日），不足一週內已有至少104人感染「不明疾病」，死者染病後2天內便會不治死亡。患者均出現嘔吐、浮腫及腹瀉等徵狀，上月底於首都阿布賈東南部的貝努埃州發現第一宗個案。"},{"pid":"562946cb3e1c2f53c195be74d03862244bb49526","tid":1876114,"uid":46685,"like":88,"dislike":2,"score":86,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T07:59:53.000Z","msg":"係咪就世界末日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bf3c8fbb2c7afa00759f7c1dbfc91de6f6359fd","tid":1876114,"uid":46685,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:00:51.000Z","msg":"好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2490d25993f5f627b263608e7163901a0a75d698","tid":1876114,"uid":46685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957617e739ab487cce3f3220e20d49690ca67bf9","tid":1876114,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:02:37.000Z","msg":"又吹大"},{"pid":"503d504bd52fafaf8b7fbe222fed81cf4830f172","tid":1876114,"uid":46685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8bacf9b1e8fea6cf39819e0c8d4258b858e6d1b","tid":1876114,"uid":46685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:03:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f0e25196fe622c261760ab620a0ec8ad2f1af3a","tid":1876114,"uid":269753,"like":169,"dislike":1,"score":168,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:04:44.000Z","msg":"瘟疫公司 online 對決.... <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859f68724a23f95e9f81133d445ef68e2038e017","tid":1876114,"uid":3063,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:04:56.000Z","msg":"新新型肺炎"},{"pid":"d2562150fcb4b022cbd0435e7db896f63b4831fb","tid":1876114,"uid":46685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:04:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21fb7c9768cbf35b229a7cdb9ccdbee71b713b16","tid":1876114,"uid":46906,"like":69,"dislike":1,"score":68,"citedBy":4,"replyT